quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,191,"waree …ìe nokku kala ka taw-…óon …ìe, yaltinee …ìe nokku ka …ìe yaltiniri on: ko geddi …óin …ìuri mawnude he dii warngo . Wota ka…ìo…óee …ìe …óo juulirde hormaande ndee haa …ìe ha…ìa on he mayre. Si …ìe ha…ìiima on ha…ìee he ma…ì…ìe. Ko hono nii woni njo…ìdi heefer…ìe …ìen."
  2,192,"Si …ìe ha…óitike, pellet, Alla ko o Hafroowo jurmotoo…óo"
  2,193,"Ka…ìo…óee …ìe haa waasa laataade fitina, diina kan laatanoo Alla. Si …ìe ha…óitike, haray jaggitere alanaa si wanaa …ìen too√±oo…ìe"
  2,194,"Si …ìe ha…ìii he mon he lewru hormaandu nduu, ha…ìee he ma…ì…ìe e lewru hormaandu nduu, kormaa…ói …óii ko njo…ìtiigu. Kala too√±…óo njo…ìto-…óee fotde ko o too√±i on . Hulee Alla anndon pellet Alla no wondi he …ìen gom…óu…ìe."
  2,195,"Mba…óee e fii laawol Alla, wata on bugor juu…óe mon …óen fa'de he halkaare. Mo∆¥∆¥inee, pellet Alla no Yi…ói mo∆¥∆¥inay…ìe …ìen."
  2,196,"Timminiree hajju oo e umra oo fii Alla. Si on sakkaama: fawike on ittugol kon ko newii e kirse, wata on femmbu ko'e mon …óen haa kirse …óen (baraa…ói) yottoo nokku majje. Kala dafaa…óo (naawnu…óo) walla lor he…ìi mo ka hoore, yo o soodtoro koorka, maa sadak maa dammol. Si on wonii he hoolaare, on mo dakmitori umra haa ka hajju: fawike mo ittugol ko newii he kirse. Mo he…ìaali (he…ìaani ), ko hoorugol bal…óe tati ka hajju e jee…ói…ói si on ruttike; …óuum ko sappo timmu…óe. Ko ja≈ãtaa koo, ko fii on taw…óo …ìeynguure mun nden laataaki ho…óu…ìe ka juulirde hormaande ndee. Hulee Alla, anndon pellet Alla ko sa…ótu…óo lepte."